Running the app:

Notes:
API server served on http://localhost:5000
React default serves on http://localhost:3000
Need to have npm, nodejs, python installed
Do not commit node_modules or python packages, they're huge

Front end:
1. cd app/seekr/
2. npm start (might need to run `npm install` to get all the packages if it doesnt work)

API server:
1. Create a virtual environment if haven't
2. Start up your virtual environment
3. While in /app folder, pip3 install -r requirements.txt
4. python app.py

Database:
WINDOWS: 
1. (if not already started) sudo service mongodb start

MAC: 
While in /app folder
1. (if not already started) mongod --dbpath=./data/db/
